stringStats.value: Glenden Wood is an Aluvian town nestled in the Tiofor Woods west of Cragstone. It was a peaceful town until Thistledown, 16 PY when the army of New Viamont invaded. Although the war between Viamontians and New Aluvia has been fought to a standstill and both sides have come to a wary truce, King Varicci's forces maintain their siege of the city.
